#L_D4_ans80=(Dalej)
#L_D4_msg90=Oh, Jason. Now I see. Now I'm completely sure confiscating this equipment is the right thing to do. You would lose it anyway - you have crab meat instead of brains. Jason is a dinAlt, a loser who just boasts of being the best gambler ever. Ask Pyrrans how much he swindled out of them in the end.
#L_D4_ans90=Hey, time out! What the hell is going on here?
