#L_D4_msg140=Shinji, Triada is not going to get this equipment, I swear! It belongs to us and no one will misappropriate it! We shall kill you all right here, if needed, but we'll have this equipment!
#L_D4_ans140=Jeez, I'm so tired of both of you. I'm delivering the cargo to Miner's Paradise, as the contract says. Then you can quarrel over it by means of litigations, lawyers or the devil himself.
#L_D4_ans141=According to the documents, Triada owns the equipment now. So I'm heading to Debris 3 and then it's not my problem anymore.
